Tonight I will be helping Raise Money for @gktwvillage .. I’ll be reading to the Children at 7pm eat .. if your interested in donating Text44321  and if your interested in watching the live stream go to my story and swipe up ❤️❤️❤️ #givingtuesdaynow

node.text: Team Buckner had such a fun weekend .. started it off with a fun movie night watching Luca and eating tons of snacks .. Saturday we had a pool day and night time playground session catching lightning bugs and today we went to the fair.. CJ had so much fun ..he saw farm animals ..played games..went on rides and now we’re ending the weekend relaxing on the couch watching tv ❤️❤️

node.text: We had ourselves a night 🍷 missing our mama J tho ❤️ #momsnightout #furmom #momof3 #momof2

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Deena Nicole Buckner on July 23, 2021. May be an image of 3 people, baby and indoor.

node.text:
Movie night with my boys ❤️ these are the moments I live for 🥰

(yes CJ is using a bottle again .. unfortunately he regressed when his baby brother came .. and I didn’t want him to feel slighted in anyway or jealous so I gave him his bottle with water in it ..he’s slowly but surely moving back to his sippy cup 🥴 our dr said it’s totally normal for this to happen )

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Deena Nicole Buckner on July 23, 2021 tagging @cbuckner_. May be an image of 2 people, baby and indoor.

node.text: Our beautiful boys ❤️ We had Cameron belly laughing this morning 🤣😩 #soblessed @cbuckner_

node.text: My two boys ❤️ my second has amazing eyebrows and my first is a soccer star 🥰

node.text: #mombun for life 🙌🏼

Cameron’s first time rolling over !!! And a video of him doing his tummy time and lifting his head above his shoulders! He’s also grabbing so well! Mommy..daddy and big brother CJ are so impressed by our little Buck ..Only 10 weeks and 3 days old 🥰 and killing it! (Stop and CJ in the first video being the cutest big brother ever 😩)
